Package: precondition
Title: Lightweight precondition, postcondition and sanity checks (aka. assertions) for R 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Taras", "Zakharko", , "taras.zakharko@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
